high_descs: Walk towards the door, then turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the rightmost candle off of the toilet tank.
Walk over to the dresser on your right.
Open the second lower drawer from the right of the dresser and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
Walk back over to the toilet on your left.
Pick up the candle off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk back over to the dresser.
Open the second lower drawer from the right of the dresser and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the toilet.
Pick up the right candle on the toilet.
Bring the candle to the counter on the right.
Put the candle away in the lower drawer below the pink rag on the counter.
Move back to the toilet to the left.
Pick up the candle on the toilet.
Bring the toilet over to the counter on the right.
Put the candle away in the lower drawer under the pink rag on the counter, right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles away in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the door, then turn right and go to the toilet.
Pick up the nail polish behind the yellow spray bottle, on the back of the toilet.
Go to the counter to your right.
Place the nail polish in the bottom third drawer to the right of the toilet.
Turn to your left and go back to the toilet.
Pick up the nail polish to the left of the yellow spray bottle, on the back of the toilet.
Turn back to the counter on your right.
Place the nail polish in the bottom, third drawer to the right of the toilet, beside the other nail polish.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of nail polish in the bathroom drawer.
